headline: Baker Hughes secures liquefaction equipment order
summary: Baker Hughes (BKR) announced an order from Bechtel Energy to supply gas technology equipment for two liquefaction plants with a total capacity of approximately 11 MTPA for Phase 1 of Woodside Energy Group (WDS) Louisiana LNG development opportunity. The order marks a significant milestone as Woodside targets final investment decision readiness from the first quarter of 2025. headline: Baker Hughes Secures Major LNG Equipment Order for Louisiana Project
summary: BKR strengthens ties with Bechtel and Woodside through a major LNG equipment order for Louisiana's Phase 1 development, aiming for FID readiness by early 2025.
